{"word":"G3411 - μισθωτός - misthōtós - mis-tho-tos' - Hired servant","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μισθωτός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">misthōtós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mis-tho-tos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hired servant</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கூலியாள் - பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"one hired, a hireling"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3409 - μισθόω - misthóō - mis-tho'-o/3409\">G3409</a>; a <i>wage worker</i> (good or bad): - hired servant, hireling.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3405/3405\">G3405</a>, <a href=\"#/G3406/3406\">G3406</a>, <a href=\"#/G3407/3407\">G3407</a>, <a href=\"#/G3408/3408\">G3408</a>, <a href=\"#/G3409/3409\">G3409</a>, <a href=\"#/G3410/3410\">G3410</a>, <a href=\"#/G3411/3411\">G3411</a>, <a href=\"#/G489/489\">G489</a>"}]}